om/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/copy-of-169-19.png\"/\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003eSource: Anker\u003c/p\u003e\n                        \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis device is sleek, compact, and powerful. It\u0026#39;s pretty much everything you\u0026#39;d want in a charging station, and its price is also quite affordable for what you\u0026#39;re getting. This model comes with two USB-A and two USB-C ports on the front, making it easy to charge phones, tablets, and even laptops as well.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eYou can do all of this because the charging station can provide up to 100W of power, which means you can pretty much charge any USB device out there without any issues. If you want, you can also plug in up to four devices at once if you\u0026#39;re in a rush to get multiple devices charged. Just be aware that the previous 100W limit will now be divided into the four ports being used. \u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eOf course, not all devices can charge via USB, which is why having AC outlets is also a must. This charging station has three AC outlets in the rear, which keeps cable clutter to a minimum. There\u0026#39;s also a long extension cable on the rear as well, making this charging station easy to maneuver when needed. \u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eIf this sounds like what you\u0026#39;re looking for, we recommend picking up this charging station for $36 while you still can. Anker is a pretty good brand when it comes to accessories and has been offering charging devices for quite some time. It even offers an 18-month warranty on this product, along with an $25,000 connected equipment warranty. \u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \n                \n        \n        \n\n\n        \n\n\n\n\n\n                    \n\n\n\n\n        \n    \u003c/article\u003e\n\n    \n            \n        \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
